{"tid":1052304,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Red Velvet YERI 將推出首支個人單曲，親自作詞、作曲！","createTime":"2019-03-08T08:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T20:06:23.000Z","uid":152432,"like":11,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"317f9409c711aadd52e502fb3071d124f901f090","tid":1052304,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:10:02.000Z","msg":"Red Velvet 成員 YERI 將透過音樂企劃「STATION」第三季發行 SOLO 自創曲《Dear Diary (스물에게)》。<br />\n<br />\nYERI 這次親自作詞作曲，歌詞描寫出她自己迎接二十歲所面臨到的古腦，特別的是，YERI 也曾在 JTBC 實境綜藝節目《只有我知道的祕密姐姐》上公開過片段，引起熱議。一直以活潑、可愛的形象受到許多喜愛的 YERI 首度推出的個人作品令粉絲們都期待不已。<br />\n<br />\n另外，音樂企劃「STATION」第三季每隔周四都會推出一首新曲，YERI 的個人創作曲《Dear Diary》將在3月14日透過各大音源網站公開。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KD0GSX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KD0GSX.jpg&h=3d008ed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5w748xY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5w748xY.jpg&h=3f784824&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64f49a1bfce8f137543e10a47b4269bb9e3c5e5f","tid":1052304,"uid":152432,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:10:31.000Z","msg":"公喜Solo"},{"pid":"4f39e0747f24c0d578d21a6179bc68e45fe24b37","tid":1052304,"uid":23363,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:10:46.000Z","msg":"我老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a0291d9207c2f3e5799fda03b72a359afcca58","tid":1052304,"uid":152432,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T08:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WDXkGTv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWDXkGTv.gif&h=73fb06ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />